<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="comb-v">comb <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kəʊm/    美 /koʊm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>梳理；搜寻：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Her mother was <strong>combing</strong> her <strong>hair</strong> carefully.
她母亲正仔细地给她梳头。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They <strong>combed</strong> (through) old newspapers and other materials <strong>for</strong> clues.
他们搜寻旧报纸和其他资料查找线索。</p><footer>2009 湖南改</footer></div></div>